# Custom API Gateway & Reverse Proxy Ingress

A bare-metal edge-routing engine built using standard Python routines to demonstrate traffic filtering and path-based request forwarding.

## 🛠️ Architectural Features
* **Reverse Proxy Mechanics:** Disguises downstream service ports, creating a unified application entry mask for connecting clients.
* **Edge Authentication Hook:** Rejects requests missing valid authorization metrics before they can penetrate deeper microservice infrastructure components.
* **Dynamic Prefix Matching:** Evaluates runtime URI route strings to seamlessly forward requests across internal networks.

